      "StatusDescriptions": {
        "Burning": "On fire. At the start of each turn, suffer 2 lethal damage per stack. Burning worsens by 1 stack each turn until extinguished.",
        "Bleeding": "Severe blood loss. At the start of each turn, suffer 1 Grazing Wound per stack until treated or stabilized.",
        "Stunned": "Disrupted by shock, impact, or overwhelming force. Each stack removes 1 AP, to a minimum of 1 AP, and halves movement.",
        "Chilled": "Extreme cold. Each stack applies -1 Movement and -5 to all tests, then fades by 1 stack each turn unless the source persists.",
        "Corroding": "Acidic exposure. At the start of each turn, suffer 2 damage per stack with armor penetration, and the corrosion worsens until neutralized.",
        "Entangled": "Physically restrained. Movement is reduced to 0 and actions suffer -5 per stack until escape.",
        "Fatigue": "Exhaustion, sleep deprivation, overexertion, or prolonged hardship. Each stack applies -5 to all tests. At 5 stacks, a Vigor Attribute Test may be required to avoid incapacitation.",
        "Prone": "On the ground. Attackers gain +10 against you, and your own attacks suffer -10 unless the target is also Prone.",
        "Fear": "A severe fear response. The exact effect and duration are determined by the Fear Table.",
        "Incapacitated": "Unable to act and removed from active combat.",
        "Dead": "Dead.",
        "LightCover": "Partially protected by terrain or obstruction. Adds +10 to defense against ranged fire when cover applies.",
        "MediumCover": "Well protected by terrain or obstruction. Adds +20 to defense against ranged fire when cover applies.",
        "HeavyCover": "Mostly protected by terrain or obstruction. Adds +30 to defense against ranged fire when cover applies."
